Package: socketeer
Title: Interface to Linux-style TCP sockets.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Martin", "Morgan",
    email = "martin.morgan@roswellpark.org",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is a simple implementation of TCP
    sockets. It provides access to client-side socket(), connect(),
    recv(), send(), and close(). It provides server-side socket(),
    bind(), listen(), select(), accept(), recv(), send(), and close().
License: Artistic-2.0
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Suggests: testthat
